title: Notes
content:
Notes may refer to:

  • Bank note, a bank certificate that represents an item or stack items of the same type
  • Patch Notes, updates documenting game changes such minor gameplay element changes and correcting graphical issues

Books[edit | edit source]

  • Alchemical notes, a book obtained during the Miss Cheevers section of the Recruitment Drive quest
  • Explorer's notes, a book written by Nestor Peregrine, and found in the Keldagrim Library
  • My notes, a book given during Barbarian Training by Otto Godblessed
  • Stronghold notes, a book that provides information about the floors in the Stronghold of Security
  • Transdimensional notes, a book that appears after defeating Vespula
  • Varmen's notes, a book that offers some insight into the Ruins of Uzer and the existence of the Golem

Other documents[edit | edit source]

  • Bervirius notes, an item obtained during the Shilo Village quest
  • Flaygian's notes, an item obtained during A Taste of Hope
  • Knight's notes, a document obtained outside the God Wars Dungeon, which explains about the godsword
  • Meeting notes, an item obtained at the end of The Giant Dwarf
  • Note (Fibonacci), an item obtained during The Feud quest
  • Note (numbers), an item obtained during The Feud quest
  • Notes (2021 Christmas event), an item obtained during the 2021 Christmas event
  • Notes (2022 Birthday event), an item obtained during the 2022 Birthday event
  • Notes, an item obtained during the Rune Mysteries quest
  • Notes 1, 2 and 3, items obtained during the Misthalin Mystery quest
  • Nulodion's notes, an item obtained during the Dwarf Cannon quest
  • Old notes, various notes of the same name used in different quests
  • Radimus notes, an item obtained at the beginning of Legends' Quest
  • Research notes, an item obtained during the Animal Magnetism quest that must be translated
  • Weiss fire notes, an item obtained during the Making Friends with My Arm quest
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
If an internal link led you to this disambiguation page, you may wish to change the link to point directly to the intended article.
